          Mazurkavägen 2, Hammarö –
          <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mazurkav%C3%A4gen+2+Hammar%C3%B6" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Maps</a>
        </li>
